Use the standard library
This is how to rescale_to_unit of numbers:
  Remember that low is item 0 in numbers
  Remember that high is item 0 in numbers
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this numbers's length times:
    When item i in numbers is less than low, then:
      Remember that low is item i in numbers
    End when
    When item i in numbers is more than high, then:
      Remember that high is item i in numbers
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that span is diff of high and low
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Add result to quotient of diff of item i in numbers and low and span
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know